Authors@R: person("Yubo", "Shao", email = "ybshao@umich.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A computationally efficient framework for penalized regression modeling of generalized linear and survival models, specifically designed to handle high-dimensional grouped effects in clustered data.
